Mukosho - unogona kunzi mupedzazviyo, mudhidhi kana horo. Ndiro buri rinoraswa naro tsvina inosara panogaiwa chikafu mudumbu, kuraswa uku kunonzi kumama asi muchishona chakavanzika kunonzi kuita tsvina. 

Zvinobuda nepamukosho zvinonhuwa samare uye zvinofanirwa kubviswa panogara vanhu nekuti zvinounza zvirwere. Kunyangwe zvawo uchibudisa zvinonhuwa kudai Mukosho unoshandiswawo neNgochani senhengo yekurarana nayo ichienzaniswa nesikarudzi yemukadzi, kurarana uku ndiko kunonzi kusvirana muchishona. Ngochani vanhu vanenge varasa hunhu pachivanhu vave kuona varume kunge vakadzi vachiteverera buri rinonhuhwa kudai

